=head3 y (y)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = -10

=head3 yM (y-MM)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 2008-02
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 1995-12
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = -10-09

=head3 yMEd (y-MM-dd - E)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 2008-02-05 - ၵၢၼ်း
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 1995-12-22 - သုၵ်း
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = -10-09-15 - သဝ်

=head3 yMMM (y MMM)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 2008 ၾႅပ်ႇ
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 1995 တီႇ
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = -10 သႅပ်ႇ

=head3 yMMMEd (y MMM d - E)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 2008 ၾႅပ်ႇ 5 - ၵၢၼ်း
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 1995 တီႇ 22 - သုၵ်း
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = -10 သႅပ်ႇ 15 - သဝ်

   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 1995 တီႇသႅမ်ႇပႃႇ
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = -10 သႅပ်ႇထႅမ်ႇပႃႇ

=head3 yMMMd (y MMM d)

   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 1995 တီႇ 22
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = -10 သႅပ်ႇ 15

   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 1995-12-22
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = -10-09-15

   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 1995 သၢမ်လိူၼ်ႁွပ်ႈ 4

=head3 yw-count-other (ဝူင်ႈထူၼ်ႈ w ၶွင်ပီ Y)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = ဝူင်ႈထူၼ်ႈ 6 ၶွင်ပီ 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = ဝူင်ႈထူၼ်ႈ 51 ၶွင်ပီ 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = ဝူင်ႈထူၼ်ႈ 37 ၶွင်ပီ -10


=head2 Miscellaneous

=head3 Prefers 24 hour time?

Yes

=head3 Local first day of the week

7 (တိတ်ႉ)

=head2 Strftime Patterns

=head3 %c (%a %b %e %H:%M:%S %Y) - date time format

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = ၵၢၼ်း ၾႅပ်ႇ  5 18:30:30 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = သုၵ်း တီႇ 22 09:05:02 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = သဝ် သႅပ်ႇ 15 04:44:23 -10

=head3 %x (%m/%d/%y) - date format

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 02/05/08
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 12/22/95
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 09/15/10

=head3 %X (%H:%M:%S) - time format

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 18:30:30
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 09:05:02
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 04:44:23

=head1 SUPPORT

See L<DateTime::Locale>.

=cut
